{"tid":152263,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"以前仲細覺得第時一定要生仔，到依家大咗覺得唔生仲好","createTime":"2017-03-11T15:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T15:48:46.000Z","uid":90505,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa370e5b379027feccdb4aa9eb239bd104a803ab","tid":152263,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"因為鐘意小朋友，而且覺得要有細路先似一頭&quot;家&quot;<br />\n以前仲諗緊幾歲生仔最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但依家香港，無論係教育制度、生活等都好大問題<br />\n冇充足既經濟能力都真係唔敢生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n害咗自己害咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但屋企人同自己個觀念由細到大都係一定要生仔<br />\n明知真係好難養，但心底裹仲係有想生既慾望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76338a9029de7bdd8eaae20c87175960d9639a16","tid":152263,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"絲打？"},{"pid":"bb5efaaa917c7492f213d6efcba08453285690f2","tid":152263,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T15:15:38.000Z","msg":"嫁個有錢人咪輕鬆冇壓力囉"},{"pid":"9b435f1f3d3f8c97edf7631cf2e0ee37d788f9dc","tid":152263,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T15:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打？</blockquote><br />\n係呀"},{"pid":"dc3555c2de7c4519d3f2964f1dfd5333db455d66","tid":152263,"uid":90505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T15:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嫁個有錢人咪輕鬆冇壓力囉</blockquote><br />\n做人實際d好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08656c3527a04b3d3ea806ef99e1bd424551a915","tid":152263,"uid":53127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>嫁個有錢人咪輕鬆冇壓力囉</blockquote><br />\n做人實際d好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢d叫現實唔係實際"},{"pid":"f5c660feff63fb8607def